title: Tiangong-1 mission in seven-hour countdown to launch
description: JIUQUAN/BEIJING， Sept. 29 (Xinhua) -- At 2:16 p.m. Beijing time (6:16 GMT)， all flight controllers at the launch center and Beijing Aerospace Flight Control Center who monitor technical systems of the Tiangong-1 mission started to check up each system's functions.
